        <p class="para">In consideration of Carolina Outfitters, Inc. furnishing services and/or equipment to participate
          in the activities or events I understand, acknowledge and agree that:</p>
        <p class="para"><b>1.) THERE ARE SIGNIFICANT INHERENT RISKS, DANGERS, AND HAZARDS COMMONLY ASSOCIATED WITH MY
