          related to any <b>INJURY, DISABILITY OR DEATH</b> I may suffer, or loss or damage to person or property,
          <b>WHETHER ARISING FROM THE NEGLIGENCE OF THE RELEASEES OR OTHERWISE</b>, that I may have presently or in the
          future to the fullest extent permitted by law. </p>
        <p class="para"><b>7.) I HAVE CAREFULLY READ THIS RELEASE OF LIABILITY AND ASSUMPTION OF RISK AGREEMENT, I FULLY
            UNDERSTAND ITS TERMS, I UNDERSTAND THAT I HAVE GIVEN UP SUBSTANTIAL RIGHTS BY SIGNING IT, AND THAT I AM
